  "comment": "F114U000A - LEDko FullSpectrum 6 HD-R: LED Ellipsoidal\n• 20-bit color mixing through 6 colors: Red, Green, Blue, Cyan, Lime, Amber\n• All whites from 2700 to 10.000 K with  CRI>95\n• 16 bit dimming electronics with 4 selectable curves (exponential,\nlogarithmic, linear and halo) digitally processed at 20 bit\n• Flicker-free operation\n• Fan setting with 4 different options (low, studio, auto, DMX regulated)\n• PowerCon True 1 In & out panel mounted connectors\n• XLR 5 Pin DMX In & out panel mounted connectors\n• Remote Device Management (RDM)\n• Max power consumption: 220 W\n• Built In Power Supply 90-250V 50/60Hz Autosensing\n•  2 mt. detachable Blue POWERCON True1 power cable with bare ends\n• Size: 362x214x210 mm (without optic)\n• Weight (with Profile zoom 15°-35° optic): 11 kg\n• Weight (with lens tube 19° optic): 9.5 kg",
